## **WWE Clash in Paris 2025 Results 08-31-2025**

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/0a72f1a1-0c88-4990-99d1-9b1facc5dd9d/14869.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_ROMAN REIGNS DEF. BRONSON REED_**
    

Pretty good match that saw Bronson Reed counter the spear with several creative reversals. Until he finally gets one and wins.

Post match Roman Reigns chokes out Paul Heyman and takes his sneakers back. He signs the sneakers and throws them into the crowd but Bron Breakker appears out of nowhere and spears Roman through a table!!!

Roman Reigns just wanted his sneakers back and now he's dead..

Reigns should never have touched Paul Heyman. Bron Breakker and Bronson Reed have ended Roman Reigns.

Spear through a table. Spear at the ring entrance.

Bron Breakker literally asks Roman if he's ready to die.

Roman gets rolled into the ring. Tsunami. Stretchered.

Reed runs back out!! Tsunami!!! Jey USO is FINALLY HERE. It's not enough. Spear to Jey. ANOTHER TSUNAMI on the stretcher.

Rest in Peace, Tribal Chief.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/771adebe-2547-47dd-9817-da3313a6b08f/14901.jpg?format=original)

