*   ## **_WWE Tag Team Championships: Wyatt Sicks def. Street Profits_**
    

Street Profits came out in Borderlands gear!!! But.... They're not getting along????

Dawkins slapped Ford across the chest and requested to get in the ring first which Ford did not seem to appreciate

The Wyatt Sicks got the win after Nikki Cross grabbed Ford's leg and Uncle Howdy hit Ford with the Sister Abigail behind the ref's back.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/6778dad4-2035-4e94-b1b7-04b8eafa3da2/14911.jpg?format=original)

