*   ## **_GOOD OL FASHIONED DONNIEBROOK MATCH: Rusev def. Sheamus_**
    

Rusev and Sheamus beat each other up in a brutal brawl across the arena. Match of the night so far that ends when Rusev makes Sheamus tap out for the second time in his entire career.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/7793007b-eb72-4c44-8305-865a8f295c1c/14919.jpg?format=original)

