*   ## **_JOHN CENA DEF. LOGAN PAUL_**
    

Unbelievable performance from John Cena and Logan Paul!!!!!!

Without a doubt Paul's greatest professional wrestling performance thus far.

The industry will be a darker place when John Cena retires this year. Thank you, Cena.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/a115c63c-67bf-4c42-b3fe-ca0af35c5264/14968.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_WWE World Heavyweight Championship: Seth Rollins def. CM Punk, LA Knight and Jey Uso_**
    

Becky Lynch just cost CM Punk the World Heavyweight Championship!!!!!!

CM Punk had Rollins up for a second GTS when a masked person hits Punk with a Low Blow. It's revealed to be Becky Lynch and then Rollins curb stomps Punk into a steel chair for the victory

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/682224f0-14b7-4a66-9f5f-fe48ddb17c7a/14969.jpg?format=original)